---

## How It Works

1. The ESP32-S3 initializes the camera and connects to Wi-Fi.
2. The camera captures a JPEG image.
3. The image is uploaded to the Flask server using an HTTP POST request.
4. The server saves the latest image.
5. The browser requests the latest image from the server and displays it.

This process repeats continuously to provide a live camera feed.

